(990, 1, '2014-12-26 07:44:58', '2014-12-26 07:44:58', 'Stewart Hotel offers a stylish and cozy accommodation in the heart of New York. The prime location of this property means that guests are just a short walk from important attractions such as Penn Station, Madison Square Garden, and New York City’s famous subway lines which make it even easier to explore more of this vibrant metropolis.\r\n\r\nStewart Hotel’s central location also makes it easy for visitors to access iconic attractions such as the Empire State Building, the art galleries in Chelsea, world-class shopping on Fifth Avenue, the live entertainment of Broadway, and the excitement of Times Square.\r\n\r\nEach guestroom at Stewart Hotel is well-equipped with the latest modern conveniences to ensure a pleasant and comfortable stay in New York City. Stewart Hotel’s convenient location and attentive staff make exploring this city an easy and enjoyable experience.', 'Stewart Hotel', '', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'stewart-hotel', '', '', '2018-12-12 10:54:31', '2018-12-12 10:54:31', '', 0, 'http://traveler.shinethemedev.com/wordpress/?post_type=hotel&#038;p=990', 0, 'st_hotel', '', 1),
